ppreciative Inquiry, Eyrolles, 2021 – JC. Barralis et S. Proust (dir), Le grand livre de l 'Appreciative Inquiry, Interéditions, 2021 15 Owen, Harrison (April 21, 2008). Open Space Technology: A User's Guide (Third ed.). Berrett-Koehler. 16 de Bryas, S, Morin. D, Bazin, P, Introduction à la pratique du Processwork, Interéditions, 2021 Photo by Mike Kononov on Unsplash